{"parentUuid":"f7eeeddb-1616-489d-a0ca-53646af4c33b","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/baotoq/Work/micro-commerce","sessionId":"204e886d-ef44-433d-8adb-f431dd47bc03","version":"2.1.72","gitBranch":"master","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01A9sDzDV6gxKELSzkpYAYLe","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the Serena MCP server instructions loaded in your session, here's what it can do:\n\n## Serena MCP — Semantic Code Intelligence\n\n### Code Exploration\n- **`get_symbols_overview`** — Get an overview of all symbols (classes, functions, methods) in a file/directory\n- **`find_symbol`** — Search for symbols by name path (e.g., `Foo/__init__`), with optional body inclusion and depth control\n- **`find_referencing_symbols`** — Find all references to a symbol across the codebase (with code snippets)\n- **`find_file`** — Locate files by name\n- **`list_dir`** — List directory contents\n- **`search_for_pattern`** — Regex/substring search across files\n\n### Code Editing (Symbolic)\n- **`replace_symbol_body`** — Replace an entire symbol's definition (method, class, function)\n- **`insert_after_symbol`** — Insert new code after a symbol (e.g., add to end of file)\n- **`insert_before_symbol`** — Insert new code before a symbol (e.g., add to start of file)\n- **`rename_symbol`** — Rename a symbol and update all references\n\n### Memory Management\n- **`list_memories`** / **`read_memory`** / **`write_memory`** — Persist notes across sessions\n- **`edit_memory`** / **`delete_memory`** / **`rename_memory`** — Manage stored memories\n\n### Project Setup\n- **`onboarding`** / **`check_onboarding_performed`** / **`initial_instructions`** — Project initialization\n\n## Key Advantage\n\nSerena avoids reading entire files. Instead it works **symbol-by-symbol** — you only fetch the bodies you actually need, which is much more token-efficient for large codebases like this one.\n\n**Example usage patterns:**\n```\n# Find a class and its methods without reading the whole file\nfind_symbol(\"CheckoutStateMachine\", include_body=false, depth=1)\n\n# Read only the specific method you need\nfind_symbol(\"CheckoutStateMachine/OnOrderPlaced\", include_body=true)\n\n# Find all places that use a type\nfind_referencing_symbols(\"OrderId\")\n```"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":22985,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":601,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":22985,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYuc7stuvRLJ4B8T2cAUH","type":"assistant","uuid":"6ed9750c-56db-4aab-a756-0c755a90b0b5","timestamp":"2026-03-10T15:05:51.589Z"}
